🔹 Procedure Question

❓ Write a procedure to display first 20 odd numbers.


---

✅ Procedure

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE first_20_odd()
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $$
DECLARE
    i INT := 1;
    cnt INT := 0;
BEGIN
    WHILE cnt < 20 LOOP
        RAISE NOTICE '%', i;
        i := i + 2;
        cnt := cnt + 1;
    END LOOP;
END;
$$;


